title: Wallaby
description: A wallaby standing on green grass, showcasing its rounded body and characteristic features such as large ears and a long tail.

title: Echidna
description: A close-up image of an echidna, a spiny anteater, foraging on green grass. The echidna has a rounded body covered in sharp spines and a long snout.

title: Student with Books
description: A young girl stands smiling, wearing a bright green t-shirt and blue jeans. She has a backpack slung over one shoulder and is holding several books in her arms. The background is plain, emphasizing her cheerful demeanor.

title: Humpback Whale
description: A close-up view of a humpback whale swimming underwater, showcasing its distinctive body shape and markings. The whale is illuminated by light, highlighting its features and the texture of its skin.
